SELECT DISTINCT L1.name
FROM likes L1
WHERE NOT EXISTS(
    SELECT *
    FROM likes L2
    WHERE L1.name != L2.name
    AND NOT EXISTS(
        SELECT *
        FROM likes L3
        WHERE L3.name = L2.name
        AND NOT EXISTS(
            SELECT *
            FROM likes L4
            WHERE L4.name = L1.name
            AND L4.beer = L3.beer))
    AND NOT EXISTS(
        SELECT *
        FROM likes L5
        WHERE L5.name = L1.name
        AND NOT EXISTS(
            SELECT *
            FROM likes L6
            WHERE L6.name = L2.name
            AND L6.beer= L5.beer)))
